\v 19 Ingaphi indlela \add lapho\add* okuhlala \add khona\add* ukukhanya? Lomnyama, ingaphi indawo yawo,
\v 20 ukuze ukuse emngceleni wakho, lokuthi uqedisise izindlela zomuzi wakho?
\v 21 Uyazi, ngoba wawusuzelwe, lenani lensuku zakho likhulu.
\v 22 Usungenile eziphaleni zeliqhwa elikhithikileyo yini, wabona iziphala zesiqhotho,
