\v 25 Ngubani owehlukanisela impophoma indlela yamanzi, lendlela yombane wemidumo,
\v 26 ukuthi line emhlabeni \add lapho\add* okungelamuntu \add khona\add*, enkangala okungelamuntu kuyo,
